    <!-- Terms of Service -->
    <string name="tos_title">Terms of Service</string>
    <string name="tos_effective_date">Jonayskie Prints — Effective January 1, 2026</string>
    <string name="tos_intro">By using Jonayskie Prints, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by the following Terms of Service.</string>
    <string name="tos_section_1">01  Acceptance of Terms\n\nBy creating an account or placing an order, you confirm that you have the legal capacity to enter into a binding agreement.</string>
    <string name="tos_section_2">02  Services Offered\n\nJonayskie Prints provides professional printing services including document printing, photocopying, scanning, photo development, and laminating.</string>
    <string name="tos_section_3">03  Payment Methods\n\nGCash is the only accepted online payment channel. Cash orders exceeding ₱500 require a 50% GCash downpayment before processing. Full GCash payment is also accepted for any order amount.</string>
    <string name="tos_section_4">04  Order Processing\n\nStandard orders are processed within 1–2 business days. Urgent requests may incur rush fees.</string>
    <string name="tos_section_5">05  File Quality\n\nCustomers are responsible for submitting print-ready files. We are not responsible for errors in the original file.</string>
    <string name="tos_section_6">06  Cancellations\n\nOrders may be cancelled prior to processing. Once production begins, cancellations are not accepted and downpayments are forfeited.</string>
    <string name="tos_section_7">07  Privacy\n\nYour personal information is used solely for order processing. We do not sell or share your data. Submitted files are deleted within 30 days of order completion.</string>
    <string name="tos_section_8">08  Prohibited Content\n\nWe reserve the right to refuse printing of any illegal, defamatory, or IP-infringing content.</string>
    <string name="tos_contact">Questions? jonalynpascual2704@gmail.com | +63 935 033 6938\nMon–Sat, 8:00 AM – 6:00 PM</string>
